        <pre class="code"><strong>VA_IMMDevice_GetId</strong>(device, device_id)   <em>; get a device id from a device pointer</em>
<em>;...</em>
device := <strong>VA_GetDevice</strong>(device_id)       <em>; get a device pointer from an id</em></pre>
